cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.LG 

The paper proposes a method for translating photos to pencil illustrations, which involves computer vision (CV) and graphics (GR) techniques. The method also involves machine learning (AI) and image processing (MM) techniques to learn separate filters for generating sketchy outlines and tonal shading. Finally, the paper evaluates the proposed algorithm using user evaluations, which involves human-computer interaction (LG).
